7.10	Jerry_Slocum	Jerry Slocum	Jerry Slocum is an American historian, collector and author specializing on the field of mechanical puzzles. Prior to retiring and dedicating his life to puzzles, he worked as an engineer at Hughes Aircraft. His personal puzzle collection, numbering over 40,000 mechanical puzzles and 4,500 books, is believed to be the world's largest.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d6/Jerry_photo-LR.jpg
